  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHAPTER 1</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Snow Melts</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an employee who has come to fill in for a friend at Jolly's Park. The park is about to close its doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO JOLLY'S PARK</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.poster.avif?t=1774050864\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.webm?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.mp4?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will return to the old Jolly's Park, and discover the mystery of the close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the mascots, turn the lights back on, and explore the park!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh, I almost forgot! Avoid Wally!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.poster.avif?t=1774050864\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.webm?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.mp4?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Wally, Berry, Whootie, Jolly and others. They are not that scary, right? Just take care, they are seeing you everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore old attractions, resolve puzzles, and don't be seen by Wally, if you want to be alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MATURE CONTENT WARNING:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Violence, fear.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHAPTER 1</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Snow Melts</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an employee who has come to fill in for a friend at Jolly's Park. The park is about to close its doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO JOLLY'S PARK</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.poster.avif?t=1774050864\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.webm?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/086a84cdbca4a704a72252c9b37c471f.mp4?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will return to the old Jolly's Park, and discover the mystery of the close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the mascots, turn the lights back on, and explore the park!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh, I almost forgot! Avoid Wally!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.poster.avif?t=1774050864\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.webm?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289600/extras/f904a51857a33b2e9c226944aa96224a.mp4?t=1774050864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Wally, Berry, Whootie, Jolly and others. They are not that scary, right? Just take care, they are seeing you everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore old attractions, resolve puzzles, and don't be seen by Wally, if you want to be alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MATURE CONTENT WARNING:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Violence, fear.</p>",
